The Postmaster of Mafdet maintains a standing commission for a complete cartographic survey of the full Saltglass Reach. While route assessments of individual corridors have been filed previously, no single comprehensive survey of the Reach's complete accessible extent exists in the harbor authority's reference archive. Traverse every section from the inland approach to the Tidemouth boundary and return with a complete route record.
Your Saltglass Reach survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority as the primary complete record of the Reach's full accessible extent. The postmaster has updated the caravan transit certification files to reference this survey as the authoritative cartographic record for the corridor.
